\newlabel{fig:3dpk}{{13}{25}{3D matter power spectrum $P(k)$ of the reconstructed initial conditions ($64^3$ lattice). The high-$k$ tail follows $P(k) \propto k^{-3.3}$ (green circles), close to the theoretical gravity scaling $k^{-3}$ (cyan dashed), despite no Fourier-space regularization in the loss function}{figure.13}{}}
